---
---
<section class="ontario-edge">
  <div class="tactile-card">
    <div class="tag">Regional Advantage</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">The Ontario Edge</h2>
    <div class="math-grid">
      <div class="math-item">
        <span class="label">ULO Charge Rate (11PM - 7AM)</span>
        <span class="value">3.9¢/kWh</span>
      </div>
      <div class="math-item">
        <span class="label">Peak Discharge Rate (4PM - 9PM)</span>
        <span class="value">39.1¢/kWh</span>
      </div>
      <div class="math-divider"></div>
      <div class="math-item profit">
        <span class="label">Automated Spread Profit</span>
        <span class="value">35.2¢/kWh</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="summary-text">
      Our AI agent automates this spread, potentially saving homeowners <span class="profit-highlight">$1,500/year</span> automatically.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .ontario-edge {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }
  
  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
  }
  
  .math-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  
  .math-item {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  
  .label {
    opacity: 0.7;
  }
  
  .value {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  
  .math-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--color-border);
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
  }
  
  .profit .label {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .profit .value {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .summary-text {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 800px;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-title { font-size: 1.8rem; }
    .math-item { font-size: 0.9rem; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.25rem; }
    .profit .value { font-size: 1.2rem; }
    .ontario-edge { padding: 0 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>
